    "description": "CDS Co.,Ltd. engages in the technical information solutions business in Japan. The company offers technical information solutions, including instruction and service manuals, digital and web/e-learning content, multilingual translation, one-source/multiple uses, consulting, and 3D-CAD design. It also provides robot solutions, including manufacturing services using robot automation systems; human resource development using industrial education and vocational training materials; and digital transformation human resource and education center services. In addition, the company offers digital solutions, including planning, development, construction, operation, and education for various systems; design, construction, and operation of IT infrastructure; system integration; system product sales; and contract control design for vehicles, aerospace, industrial machinery mechatronics, distribution and logistics, energy, and education sectors. The company was incorporated in 1980 and is headquartered in Okazaki, Japan."
